{"id":231920234,"title":"外食清洗餐具的方法","content":"先來介紹我的外食餐具好夥伴\n第一個是等等要介紹的清洗工具\n第二和第三都是由校內的草地音樂會拿到的好用餐具\nhttp://i.imgur.com/KmhheD1.jpg\n我在網路上看了不少大家的清洗方式\n大多都是用分裝瓶\n但我偏好用海綿洗餐具\n於是我突發奇想\n就用夾鏈袋裝海綿及洗碗精水\n這樣就能在外用海綿清洗餐具了\n也許有人會吐槽說夾鏈袋不環保\n只要小心使用，別讓袋子破損，使袋子能重複使用就能不浪費\nhttp://i.imgur.com/GzHsdQM.jpg\n推薦這招給大家\n不知道有沒有人跟我用一樣的方法?","excerpt":"先來介紹我的外食餐具好夥伴，第一個是等等要介紹的清洗工具，第二和第三都是由校內的草地音樂會拿到的好用餐具，我在網路上看了不少大家的清洗方式，大多都是用分裝瓶，但我偏好用海綿洗餐具，於是我突發奇想，就用","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-08-23T10:58:40.485Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-23T10:58:55.736Z","commentCount":11,"likeCount":45,"tags":[],"topics":["無痕飲食","環保","清洗","洗碗精","方便"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"國立臺東大學","department":"資訊工程學系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":45}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/KmhheD1.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/GzHsdQM.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"f5ce890f-03b9-41de-8eb1-7409e7062d4a","url":"https://i.imgur.com/KmhheD1l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/KmhheD1l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/KmhheD1l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-23T10:58:40.485Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-23T10:58:55.736Z"},{"id":"f5ce890f-03b9-41de-8eb1-7409e7062d4a","url":"http://i.imgur.com/KmhheD1.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/KmhheD1","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/KmhheD1l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-23T10:58:40.485Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-23T10:58:55.736Z"},{"id":"128b7748-23e1-4d28-a294-35afba75b860","url":"http://i.imgur.com/GzHsdQM.jpg","normalizedUrl"